WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.440
Give browser agents context before they click.

2
00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:05.160
Inject the runtime and wait for the proof surface to settle.

3
00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:08.360
Apply the dense capture preset that turns on the full runtime surface.

4
00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:11.160
Read the live runtime contract instead of guessing what the page exposes.

5
00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:14.120
Build a structured JSON report from the live runtime state.

6
00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:17.080
Turn the same runtime state into a readable handoff report.

